strife in the world to see two
great world

25:21.186 --> 25:27.593 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
leaders come together and begin
more -- perhaps
more formally, a dialogue.

25:27.693 --> 25:29.495 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Your Eminence,
why now?

25:29.595 --> 25:31.497 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARDINAL THEODORE MCCARRICK,
Archbishop of
Washington, D.C.: Well, I think
it's special

25:31.597 --> 25:35.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
for many reasons, as the
beatitude mentioned
many of them.

25:35.134 --> 25:40.906 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
