the days of
communism.

26:03.128 --> 26:09.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so, that's all passed now,
and the church
has come into its own. And we
see so many

26:09.768 --> 26:15.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
