those years
coming back and very fervently
and very wonderfully

26:15.407 --> 26:20.612 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
saying, we are Orthodox
Christians, we know
who we are.

26:20.712 --> 26:25.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So what a great time to do it.
It's a good
moment because there are a lot
of good things

26:25.384 --> 26:29.021 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
happening, and it's a good
moment because
there are a lot of bad things
happening, and

26:29.121 --> 26:31.390 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
we all have to stay together
more than we
ever have before.

26:31.490 --> 26:34.126 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And what are
some of the
bad things? What are the
concerns that your

26:34.226 --> 26:36.128 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
two churches agree on?

26:36.228 --> 26:42.768 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THE MOST BLESSED TIKHON: Well,
certainly,
I think what you will see from
the joint declaration

26:42.868 --> 26:48.106 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
from today's meeting, the
persecution of Christians
in the Middle East.

26:48.207 --> 26:54.179 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
