that all the

28:34.846 --> 28:36.782 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
time: I want you to be one.

28:36.882 --> 28:42.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so, as we look around now,
with all the
troubles, with all the
difficulties, with

28:42.154 --> 28:47.159 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
all the persecutions in so many
parts of the
world, this is the time to be
together. This

28:47.259 --> 28:54.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is the time to say, we are
together. If there's
any time when we want to get
together and

28:54.566 --> 28:59.271 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
embrace each other in our faith,
that time
