28:59.371 --> 29:04.776 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Your
Beatitude, it seems
that, back then, there were
political concerns.

29:04.876 --> 29:11.516 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now there are also political
concerns, especially
in regions like Russia and the
Ukraine.

29:11.617 --> 29:17.923 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How do churches put this behind
them and say,
for the greater good, we need to
make these

29:18.023 --> 29:23.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
compromises and we need to --
