a 1,000-year horizon, not just
who's elected

29:23.729 --> 29:25.530 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
next?

29:25.631 --> 29:29.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THE MOST BLESSED TIKHON: I think
