30:15.313 --> 30:19.851 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, really, those personal
contexts are really
crucial.

30:19.951 --> 30:22.487 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Same question
to you.

30:22.587 --> 30:28.660 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARDINAL THEODORE MCCARRICK:
It's a world
whose horrors call for harmony
among those

30:28.760 --> 30:30.929 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
